snippet: Justin Gatlin won the 100 meters at the Prefontaine Classic in Eugene, Ore., in a wind-aided time of 9.88 seconds, besting his fellow Americans Michael Rodgers and Ryan Bailey.
abstract: American sprinter Justin Gatlin wins 100 meters at Prefontaine Classic in Eugene, Ore., in a wind-aided time of 9.88 seconds;
